A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act providing for the election of the Board of Education of Gwinnett County,
2 approved April 7, 1972 (Ga. L. 1972, p. 4058), as amended, particularly by an Act approved
3 May 6, 2005 (Ga. L. 2005, p. 3818), so as to revise provisions regarding the compensation
4 of members of the board of education; to provide for the suspension of such provisions in the
5 event of such board approving a buyout of the superintendent's contract; to prohibit the
6 infringement of communications made by members of the such board; to provide exceptions;
7 to provide for related matters; to provide for an effective date; to repeal conflicting laws; and
8 for other purposes.
9 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
10 SECTION 1.
11 An Act providing for the election of the Board of Education of Gwinnett County, approved
12 April 7, 1972 (Ga. L. 1972, p. 4058), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May 6,
13 2005 (Ga. L. 2005, p. 3818), is amended by revising Section 2 and adding a new section to
14 read as follows:
